{"tid":580341,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"無知一問 哈布斯堡家族點壟斷到神聖羅馬帝國皇位？","createTime":"2018-03-04T12:27:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-06T14:05:30.000Z","uid":2720,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"5e86585e410e2b15274b8f6597ac4baed624b605","tid":580341,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"十四世紀查理四世確立選帝候制度 最初有七位選帝候 後來先後再加兩位 九位選帝候一直維持到1803年 但點解哈布斯堡可以由盧森堡手中拎到帝位後幾乎壟斷帝位直至帝國解散 點樣控制每一次投票結果？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259cd9b46ad7551ba1a041574e58f90ac881e871","tid":580341,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T13:42:56.000Z","msg":"有冇熟中世紀歐陸歷史嘅巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80ceb54744ecb4f50bf15a8648a700b2c504f88b","tid":580341,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T14:07:02.000Z","msg":"下半身征服歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e6d061bca7bdefd056002e42db551415b79b216","tid":580341,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"80ceb54744ecb4f50bf15a8648a700b2c504f88b","tid":580341,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T14:07:02.000Z","msg":"下半身征服歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-04T14:38:48.000Z","msg":"我知佢地聯姻出名 但有三席選帝候係大主教 到底係憑咩令其他選帝候唔同佢爭/投佢票? 就算因爲聯姻投你票 都唔可能維持幾百年一直投票畀你掛 其他家族唔會唔想爭坐皇帝位下化 尤其係其他選帝候 但皇位真係畀人搶走只係短暫咁出現過一次"},{"pid":"f167ede1bbd82a22a979adac7c246428766550e5","tid":580341,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T04:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa7f64f6842639f0229e377d3dda1b7037d8fb9","tid":580341,"uid":61882,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下半身征服歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我知佢地聯姻出名 但有三席選帝候係大主教 到底係憑咩令其他選帝候唔同佢爭/投佢票? 就算因爲聯姻投你票 都唔可能維持幾百年一直投票畀你掛 其他家族唔會唔想爭坐皇帝位下化 尤其係其他選帝候 但皇位真係畀人搶走只係短暫咁出現過一次</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/79/Albrecht-von-Brandenburg-2.jpg/220px-Albrecht-von-Brandenburg-2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fthumb%2F7%2F79%2FAlbrecht-von-Brandenburg-2.jpg%2F220px-Albrecht-von-Brandenburg-2.jpg&h=26fea5cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿爾布雷希特&middot;馮&middot;勃蘭登堡<br />\n當時勃蘭登堡選帝侯個細仔<br />\n因為係細仔所以選帝侯個位就冇佢份喇<br />\n但係佢又想做吓選民喎咁點算好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n於是佢就問當時係歐洲富可敵國既富格家族借咗一大筆錢黎&ldquo;疏通&rdquo;<br />\n等佢可以做到美茵茨大主教<br />\n從而攞到選帝侯既資格<br />\n之後佢為咗還錢<br />\n就係佢既教區賣贖罪券<br />\n跟住辣著埋個痴線佬<br />\n再之後就係持續百年既宗教戰爭...<br />\n你話佢搞咁多花臣都要做選帝侯<br />\n會唔會淨係為咗投吓票過癮吓咁呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57fa6fc04f05baf1640f9ede65612cfa98575ea4","tid":580341,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T04:54:16.000Z","msg":"舊時奧地利柒足咁多年都keep到個國家地位都算幾勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd29c79faa16b5a5ee82a288efd120f14078f9d2","tid":580341,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T04:56:53.000Z","msg":"lm學田弓"},{"pid":"cd7228d9ce5058e975bd0eae1289107429a9b78c","tid":580341,"uid":2720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bfa7f64f6842639f0229e377d3dda1b7037d8fb9","tid":580341,"uid":61882,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>下半身征服歐洲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>我知佢地聯姻出名 但有三席選帝候係大主